  "text": "The mixed state E R can be realized by sampling random wave functions φ uniformly from the unit sphere in H R . When dim H R is much larger than dim H S , concentration of measure for high-dimensional spheres implies that the random substate Tr E |φ φ| is very close to the average substate Ω S with high probability [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
